1. What's this?
   This is a simple Java Socket communication demo. Server side receive 'Test Success' notification hints test success, network connection is okay.
2. How to run?
   1) run server side:
      java -jar socket-conn-v2.jar server -b 10.66.192.144 -p 1099
   2) run client side:
     java -jar socket-conn-v2.jar client -b 10.66.192.144 -p 1099
